<P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#dcdeed><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/urelkeb.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Relkeb</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>6</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#333333>4/12/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#333333>11:34:34 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B>&nbsp<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: SOTS, KEG, Public - Community effort. Need input </font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I'm in probably what would be called a medium size guild of about 60 people.  We have about 20 very experienced planar folks, and about 15 more in the low 40's chomping at the bit.  Back on the Rathe with 2 other guilds, scheduled Fear and Hate once each per month and hand no problem clearing them and have a god kill (old inny) under our belt.<br>
