<P><i><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/urelkeb.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Relkeb</A> at: 4/12/01 11:38:06 am</FONT><br></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#989dca><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/ucaesiumshadowblade.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Caesium Shadowblade</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>The Grouch</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>14</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#333333>4/12/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#333333>11:36:41 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://facelink.com/edit/raw/rawimage/05/1508005.gif?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B>&nbsp<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: SOTS, KEG, Public - Community effort. Need input </font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Uh Bane, were you even on E'ci? I think your interpretation of events happening there are somewhat distorted and one sided. <br>
<br>
