<br>
One of the big advantages of a guild is that we can adapt.  We can plan on going to Hate, find Icewind there, and shift gears and rush to Trakanon.  Nobody minds too much.  They understand Icewind got there first and they know that if the situations were reversed, Icewind would head off to some second goal.  We also know that if we don't get Hate today, we might get it next month and that if we get Trak today, it still helps the guild.  <br>
<br>
